caption.p: 2-DE images of gels from three experimental groups. ( A) Healthy pulp group. ( B) Inflamed pulp group. ( C) Traumatic pulp group. Green circles indicate the spots that were excised for mass spectrometry. A, type II keratin; B, annexin V chain A; C, mutant beta-actin; D, hemoglobin chain B; E, hemoglobin chain A; F, hemoglobin alpha 1-2 hybrid.
